{"tid":296053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 無印嘅擦膠到底咩構造？","createTime":"2017-06-24T09:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T10:16:41.000Z","uid":114271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e4183d93c55be51eb73c4c0bb6993819968a807","tid":296053,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:18:50.000Z","msg":"話說 今日同個學生私補個陣<br />\n預備左d grammar練習俾佢做<br />\n有份因爲舊學生做過就冇再印過份新<br />\n於是我襯住個學生畫mindmap嘅時候起勢咁擦撚晒佢<br />\n擦完成枱都係擦膠碎<br />\n<br />\n因為唔係咁好意思要人清潔嘅關係<br />\n我即刻用純熟嘅手法將d擦膠碎堆埋一堆<br />\n當住我學生面一把間尺達落去<br />\n然後起勢卒成長條型<br />\n再用手指公磋磋磋<br />\n根據我小學時累積返黎嘅經驗<br />\n應該好快會變成完美球狀<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/24/171523_ad118dd9c55db8525918ab3589508ecd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F24%2F171523_ad118dd9c55db8525918ab3589508ecd.jpg&h=211873fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢舊磋極都岩岩慚慚<br />\n極大挫敗感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宜家我啱啱補完習去搭火車<br />\n途中我會一路行一路繼續磋<br />\n有咩再向大家匯報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838ec2f80a41b28239cf75d0fa4bf5ea0ff15878","tid":296053,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:28:31.000Z","msg":"應該用多D時間就會變泥膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我細個都係玩開黑色正方柱個D擦膠 未用過無印"},{"pid":"eb1175dd39e0dca110da35831af7a31dab402eec","tid":296053,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該用多D時間就會變泥膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我細個都係玩開黑色正方柱個D擦膠 未用過無印</blockquote><br />\n由補完習行去火車站嘅路程已經磋左唔少時間<br />\n汗水已經同擦膠碎混和為一體<br />\n <img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/24/173359_0de9cff102399c08fb04a3776dc5c0af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F24%2F173359_0de9cff102399c08fb04a3776dc5c0af.jpg&h=b79d7fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n磋到成粒八仙果咁都係咁多裂痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3536bd5f2c6e1aa2b29f0b49cd56eb0c21efc39","tid":296053,"uid":12124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:37:22.000Z","msg":"天氣太乾, 加d水"},{"pid":"a5a98fd530696fe49c8d695d40a58ce5470e285a","tid":296053,"uid":114271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天氣太乾, 加d水</blockquote><br />\n加左好多汗水 唔work<br />\n已經壓縮到咩型都磋到出黎嘅狀態 <br />\n都係一樣咁多裂痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9365fc5e9b5c97d9a865aec57882d4e8b102e3f8","tid":296053,"uid":107913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>天氣太乾, 加d水</blockquote><br />\n加左好多汗水 唔work<br />\n已經壓縮到咩型都磋到出黎嘅狀態 <br />\n都係一樣咁多裂痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n射d精落去, 強化表層, 修補裂痕"},{"pid":"e26b8701996245f314f862c4be6cedd32cfb538e","tid":296053,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>天氣太乾, 加d水</blockquote><br />\n加左好多汗水 唔work<br />\n已經壓縮到咩型都磋到出黎嘅狀態 <br />\n都係一樣咁多裂痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n射d精落去, 強化表層, 修補裂痕</blockquote><br />\n返到屋企搵J圖試試佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537db4bd27612fa83b34c0c5553bcd03cf8f88bd","tid":296053,"uid":16120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T09:59:29.000Z","msg":"無印搓唔到<br />\nPilot 最好搓"},{"pid":"c95b60deaafb7c6a189f4d43afc91cbc0d71326f","tid":296053,"uid":12625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited